data.description: Penthouse living with the Florida lifestyle.  This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath condo in the salt water community,  has a beautiful balcony patio overlooking the canal.  Kitchen overlooking the family room area and windows all around for natural sunlight.  LVP throughout with Tile in the wet areas, large family/living room area which is great for entertaining.  Master suite has plenty of space with a nice size walk in closet.  This condo also features 3 storage rooms, 1 is room situated next to the unit, 2 parking spaces, a Keegan Water purifier and a mold detector.
